\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\s28\sl240\slmult1\itap0{\s28\f0\fs24\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch Once in a while tilt the skillet in various directions to ensure that the melted butter has}{\s28\f0\fs24\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\s28\sl240\slmult1\itap0{\s28\f0\fs24\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch reached all corners of the pan. If it does not, add more butter. To create the perfect pan}{\s28\f0\fs24\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
